{
  "texts": [
    "It is based on experimental measurements that yield unbiased results.",
    "We have designed a scoring mechanism that evaluates the SIEM solutions on the basis of their level of implementation of a set of important features.",
    "The scoring mechanism is developed by keeping in view the requirements of SMEs.",
    "Our evaluation methodology comprises 1) Performance evaluation and 2) Feature evaluation.",
    "The performance of a SIEM system is normally measured in terms of EPS, which is the number of events that can be processed per second."
  ]
}